title: SEMA 2015: Flowmaster Sounds Off with Modern Muscle Applications

asset.title: SEMA 2015: Flowmaster Sounds Off with Modern Muscle Applications
asset.description:
The "Flowmaster sound" is an inseparable part of the classic musclecar experience, but they've got modern pony cars covered too. They've rolled out new resonator delete systems to join their existing exhausts for 2015-up Mustangs, and they've already got axle-back Outlaw exhausts and American Thunder dual mode systems ready to go for the soon-to-be-released 2016 Camaro.
